result.name: CHAO PHRAYA

reviews.text: Doesn't taste good

Went there for afternoon 'tea' set. Staffs (two Thai ladies) were friendly. I Ordered Thai pork knuckle rice with Thai iced milk tea. The meat was juicy, soft and succulent. Though some people may not like the sweet soya sauce as it could be a bit too sweet for some people but personally I think it went well with rice. Good portion for me as late lunch. Value for money. Recommended :)
Good Tai cuisine, reasonable price, good service
